data.description: Welcome to 136 S. Wrens Way - This custom, private oasis has SO much to offer both inside and out! As you climb the stairs and enter the front door you're greeted by an overflow of natural light pouring through the open floor plan.  The living room is perfectly sized for those family gatherings around the fireplace and sits just adjacent to combination dining room/kitchen and sliders off the kitchen to a separate deck for morning coffee. Down the hall are  2 bedrooms and a full bath and the entire 3rd floor is the primary bedroom with en suite bathroom it's own private deck.  Heating and A/C units are less than 1 year old! An 18 X 30 salt water pool with the entire 1.32 acres fenced in. The privacy of the pool and additional decking adds the the ambiance of this beautiful property.  There is a huge bonus room attached to the garage that is 25 X 20 (Potential man cave/she shed) You won't find anything else like this.  It's truly unique and a must see.  Located near Killens Pond State campground and about 30 minutes to the beaches. Schedule your tour today! SHOWINGS BEGIN FRIDAY!
